{"tid":2291191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★又贏！綜援等社福津貼明年2月料加2.8%　高額長生津增至$3819","createTime":"2020-11-18T14:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T10:35:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08769d244ecc686ab16952dad6b016a957d06ddc","tid":2291191,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"127萬名公共福利及綜援人士明年可望增加津貼2.8%，而綜援租金津貼最高金額亦可望上調1.6%。公共福利金計劃津貼若以2.8%調升，高額長者生活津貼會由現時3715港元，增加104港元升至3819港元；普通長者生活津貼將由2,770港元，增加78港元，至2848港元，共有約59萬名長者受惠。<br />\n<br />\n公共福利金若以2.8%調升，俗稱生果金的高齡津貼會由1435港元，加約40港元升至1475港元。普通及高額傷殘津貼分別由1835港元及3670港元，升至約1886港元及3773港元。至於綜援標準金額，單身健全成人會由現時2615港元加至約2688港元。<br />\n<br />\n現時綜援住戶可獲發租金津貼，最高金額由1人的2475港元至6人或以上的7675港元，計及2020年7月1日起生效的一次性加幅，及根據租金指數1.6%上調，將加至2,515港元至7,800港元，增加40港元至125港元不等。<br />\n<br />\n是次調整分別按今年9月底的社會保障援助物價指數及租金指數的12個月移動平均數累積升幅計算津貼的上調空間。政府計劃今年12月按社援指數的最新數字，向財委會尋求批准相關撥款。如獲財委會批准，相關津貼額將由明年2月1日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201117/bkn-20201117210212774-1117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201117%2Fbkn-20201117210212774-1117_00822_001.html&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=edf33e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201117/bkn-20201117210212774-1117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"def240d420e32dcf47bf361fa21111d7456af44e","tid":2291191,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d90a56c898db7dbb8235cf5ce7dc01bbd6254c","tid":2291191,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"廢老或成最終贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa48d6dad47b1a257697f30d81d21e2b283cc14f","tid":2291191,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdkW2LH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdkW2LH.png&h=4e75bbfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"343798515e8746d6933fd0b82a90828feb981111","tid":2291191,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69d90a56c898db7dbb8235cf5ce7dc01bbd6254c","tid":2291191,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"廢老或成最終贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANGr2GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGr2GX.png&h=017d56af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ad545893d478ecf8d048b3f6a9b96060ec6c31a","tid":2291191,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"fatfat<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qqwcdOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqqwcdOr.jpg&h=eb0a2599&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adbd4af88f8d74548584b6ac08cf6d04cb9376ae","tid":2291191,"uid":366470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"腥港人同廢老跑贏大市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人出年平均加薪先得嗰1%都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886e44c731f4e5b6487945ecd8cb8125d5ab8786","tid":2291191,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"連月疫情影響本地就業市場，有求職平台調查發現，本地僱主預期明年為僱員加薪僅0.8%，創10年新低。整